  26 Jun 2010; Christoph Mende <angelos@gentoo.org> xwax-0.7.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #323501

*xwax-0.7 (08 Mar 2010)

  08 Mar 2010; Joe Sapp <nixphoeni@gentoo.org> +xwax-0.7.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Version bump; added XWAX_DECODERS to IUSE so RDEPEND (and the xwax-import
  script) can be setup properly to handle the audio files the user cares
  about; bumped EAPI for access to EROOT

  09 Feb 2010; Joseph Jezak <josejx@gentoo.org> xwax-0.5.ebuild,
  xwax-0.6-r1.ebuild:
  Marked ppc/ppc64 stable for bug #293240.

  06 Jan 2010; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> xwax-0.6-r1.ebuild:
  Marking xwax-0.6-r1 ~ppc64 for bug 276855

  19 Nov 2009; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> xwax-0.6-r1.ebuild:
  amd64/x86 stable, bug #293240

  19 Nov 2009; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> xwax-0.5.ebuild:
  amd64/x86 stable, bug #293240

  15 Nov 2009; Joe Sapp <nixphoeni@gentoo.org> -xwax-0.4.ebuild,
  -xwax-0.6.ebuild:
  Removed old ebuilds

*xwax-0.6-r1 (20 Sep 2009)

  20 Sep 2009; Joe Sapp <nixphoeni@gentoo.org> +xwax-0.6-r1.ebuild,
  +files/xwax-0.6-execlp.patch:
  Added patch from Yves Adler
  (http://sourceforge.net/mailarchive/message.php?msg_name=4AB236E1.3090001%
  40googlemail.com) to search for extra binaries (xwax_import and xwax_scan)
  in the PATH environment variable if they aren't found in the current
  directory.

  08 Sep 2009; Joe Sapp <nixphoeni@gentoo.org> xwax-0.4.ebuild,
  xwax-0.5.ebuild, xwax-0.6.ebuild:
  Only the optimization levels should be removed from CFLAGS and LDFLAGS to
  allow for user customization

*xwax-0.6 (08 Sep 2009)

  08 Sep 2009; Joe Sapp <nixphoeni@gentoo.org> +xwax-0.6.ebuild:
  Version bump

*xwax-0.5 (07 Jul 2009)

  07 Jul 2009; Joe Sapp <nixphoeni@gentoo.org> +xwax-0.5.ebuild:
  Revision bump

  07 Jun 2009; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> xwax-0.4.ebuild:
  Use tc-export to respect CC.

  07 Jun 2009; Joe Sapp <nixphoeni@gentoo.org> xwax-0.4.ebuild:
  Changed exeinto/doexe to dobin and added '|| die' to verify it worked

  07 Jun 2009; Joe Sapp <nixphoeni@gentoo.org> xwax-0.4.ebuild:
  Fixed src_install() that was broken on update to EAPI 2

  15 Sep 2008; Pieter Van den Abeele <pvdabeel@gentoo.org> xwax-0.4.ebuild:
  Keyworded ~ppc. Closes #237590

